                     <interp inst="t18470201-539-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 32 yards of damask, value 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; and 36 yards of drill, 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18470201-name-453" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470201-name-453" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
