                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant</hi> N 14.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction at Clerkenwell, last March—I was present when he was convicted—he is the man—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 17th March, 1846, and confined two months.</hi>)</p>
